snippet.title: Amber Schulz | Convos Over Cold Brew #77
snippet.description:
In this episode Emma sits down with Amber Schulz, a high school senior XC/track runner with a strong and positive presence on social media, for a second time. They talk about Amber's growth as a person over the last year and a half, committing to run at High Point University, updates on her injury, finding herself outside of running and more!
